Data Analyst Roadmap
Tip
by Viet Anh
- When you're learning these tools, if you come up with an idea that you'd like to do, feel free to divert from the roadmap and try working on your idea first.

- Don't spend too much time on one topic. Getting the bigger picture is more important.

- If you want to learn another skill which is not on this list, feel free to do so. Research about the skill to see if they are in demand, and plan your time and effort accordingly.
This is a simple and very overviewing roadmap of essential skills to learn for becoming a data analyst.



SQL & Excel
Power BI & Statistics
Python & ML/AI
Interact with data sources
Transform and visualise data
Program & automate process
